  "response": "It's not advisable to strive for being \"stupid.\" Instead, it's more beneficial to focus on personal growth, learning, and understanding. Everyone makes mistakes or has moments of confusion, and that\u2019s part of being human. If you're feeling overwhelmed or unsure about something, it might help to ask questions, seek guidance, or simply take a break to clear your mind. Embracing curiosity and striving to learn will always serve you better than trying to be less informed.",
